# Cursor Rules for Krystallise Project

## Frontend Build Rule
- When any changes are made to files in the `frontend/` folder, automatically run `npm run build` in the frontend directory to compile and build the project.
- This ensures the frontend is always up-to-date and ready for deployment after modifications.

## General Development Guidelines
- Follow existing design patterns in the project when creating new components
- Always examine backend code to understand front-end/back-end contracts
- Use consistent styling with existing components
- Maintain TypeScript type safety throughout the codebase
